Senator Iroegbu in Abuja The Inspector General of Police (IGP), Ibrahim Idris, has directed the Senate President, Senator Bukola Saraki, to report to the head of the Force Intelligence Response Team at Guzape, Abuja on Tuesday for further investigation over the April 5 Offa bank robberies. Idris in a statement he personally signed on Monday noted that Saraki’s earlier response to Police was not satisfactory. Details later…